                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001029-45-off251 t18001029-45-cd252"></join>, an iron bar, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18001029-45-victim380" type="victimName">
                     Richard James Thomas 
                     Weatherhead
